  m_Text: The player is tasked with navigating Faby through pairs of pipes that have
    equally sized gaps placed at random heights. Faby automatically descends and
    only ascends when the player taps the touchscreen. Each successful pass through
    a pair of pipes awards the player one point. Colliding with a pipe or the ground
    ends the gameplay.
